name: Morud
description: $MORUD is a memecoin that humorously pays tribute to Murad Mahmudov, a prominent figure on X recognized for his unwavering belief in specific meme coins. The project combines entertainment with crypto, aiming to build a community through creative animations that reflect Murad's top convictions. With a dedicated team of marketers, designers, and leaders, $MORUD strives to create a unique and engaging memecoin experience.
